^m (h_&amp;theta;(x^{(i)}) - y^{(i)}) x_j^{(i)} \\newline &amp; \\rbrace \\end{align*}\nA vectorized implementation is:\n$$\\theta := \\theta - \\frac{\\alpha}{m} X^{T} (g(X \\theta ) - \\vec{y})$$\n<!-- more -->\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</nil>\n"}
